(96, 'Représentant Commercial France (H/F) - Dakar', 'Webtel, agence d’externalisation de forces de vente spécialisée dans les métiers du sport, recherche un  Représentant Commercial France (H/F)  de Secteur dynamique et passionné pour représenter une marque Française d’équipements de sports de combat.    Missions :     Passionné et pratiquant de sport, vous avez un tempérament commercial et une aisance relationnelle. Il est temps pour vous d’allier passion et carrière professionnelle en nous rejoignant !  Rattaché à la direction commerciale France, vous serez en charge d\'optimiser la présence de la marque et son chiffre d\'affaires sur le secteur auprès d\'une clientèle de magasins multimarques textile indépendants, de chausseurs et de...', 'WEBTEL', 'Région de :Dakar', 'https://www.emploisenegal.com/offre-emploi-senegal/representant-commercial-france-hf-dakar-1230276', 'emploisenegal.com', '2024-12-02', '2025-01-06 18:00:39.091315', 'Non spécifié', 'Expérience entre 2 ans et 5 ans et plus', 'Contrat proposé\n                             :CDI', 'Actions Commerciales - Maintenance - Merchandising - Prospection - Qualité - Suivi des Ventes - Vente'),
(97, 'Prestataire Indépendant Senior Commercial, Business Developer - Dakar', 'Une entreprise leader dans le secteur de la beauté et du bien-être au Sénégal recherche un  Senior Commercial, Business Developer   pour ses trois points de vente physiques. Ce profil stratégique intégrera la Direction Commerciale BtoC et jouera un rôle clé dans le développement et l’animation des ventes en magasin. Nous recherchons une personne passionnée par la performance, animée par l\'atteinte des objectifs, et disposant d’une forte  expertise en service client de luxe .     Missions Principales    1.  Développement Commercial et Animation des Points de Vente :     Identifier et mettre en œuvre des stratégies de développement commercial pour accroître la fréquentation et les ventes dans...', 'MK WELLNESS & BEAUTY', 'Région de :Dakar & International', 'https://www.emploisenegal.com/offre-emploi-senegal/prestataire-independant-senior-commercial-business-developer-dakar-1222147', 'emploisenegal.com', '2024-12-02', '2025-01-06 18:00:39.097039', 'Non spécifié', 'Etudiant, jeune diplômé et plus', 'Contrat proposé\n                             :Freelance', 'Animation des Ventes - Développement Commercial - Vente'),
(98, 'Stagiaire Marketing & IT - Data Analyst Junior  - Dakar', 'Une entreprise majeure dans le secteur de la beauté et du bien-être au Sénégal recherche un  Stagiaire Marketing & IT - Data Analyst Junior  pour renforcer sa stratégie digitale et optimiser ses ventes en ligne. Ce stagiaire rejoindra notre Digital, pour accélérer notre présence digitale et maximiser nos performances commerciales, promouvoir l’image de plusieurs marques sur le marché sénégalais et renforcer la satisfaction client à travers les canaux physiques et digitaux.     Objectif du Poste :     Sous la supervision d’un maitre de stage, le stagiaire aura pour mission d’analyser les données pour optimiser les activités commerciales de l’entreprise. Il contribuera activement au succès des...', 'MK WELLNESS & BEAUTY', 'Région de :Dakar & International', 'https://www.emploisenegal.com/offre-emploi-senegal/stagiaire-marketing-it-data-analyst-junior-dakar-1221050', 'emploisenegal.com', '2024-12-02', '2025-01-06 18:00:39.101033', 'Non spécifié', 'Etudiant, jeune diplômé et plus', 'Contrat proposé\n                             :Stage', 'BI'),
(99, 'Commercial Senior  - Dakar', 'Nous sommes à la recherche d’un  Commercial Senior.     Missions :    Le candidat retenu aura pour rôle de :   Développer le portefeuille client  Développer les ventes des clients déjà acquis  Assurer le recouvrement de toutes les ventes effectuées et la prospection de nouveaux clients  S’assurer du suivi des livraisons  S’assurer de la bonne documentation de toutes les ventes  S’assurer de la bonne gestion des stocks au sein du dépôt en collaboration avec l’ADV  Effectuer la promotion des divers produits de l’Entreprise  Fidéliser les clients  Prospecter les nouveaux clients  Gérer de manière optimale le budget dédié aux dépenses du dépôt  Effectuer une veille concurrentielle quotidienne et...', 'PCG AFRICA', 'Région de :Dakar', 'https://www.emploisenegal.com/offre-emploi-senegal/commercial-senior-dakar-1207679', 'emploisenegal.com', '2024-12-02', '2025-01-06 18:00:39.104886', 'Non spécifié', 'Expérience entre 2 ans et 5 ans et plus', 'Contrat proposé\n                             :CDD', 'Prospection - Recouvrement - Vente'),
(100, 'ANGULAR Developer (M/F)', 'We are looking for  ANGULAR Developer  profiles / CVs to pass on to our clients for their future recruitment campaigns. \n   \n  Mission:  \n   \n \n	 Working within a Team to determine needs and applying / customizing existing technology to meet those needs. \n	 Producing detailed specifications and writing the program codes that perform efficiently. \n	 Write clean, scalable, reusable code using ANGULAR framework such as LumX, NGX-Bootstrap, Vue.js etc. \n	 Be responsible for providing technical guidance or solutions. \n	 Define, advocate, and implement best practices and coding standards for the team. \n	 Develop and guide the team members in enhancing their technical capabilities and increasing productivity. \n	 Manage, train...', 'AFRICASHORE', 'Région de :Dakar - Diourbel - Fatick - Kaffrine - Kaolack - Kédougou - Kolda', 'https://www.emploisenegal.com/offre-emploi-senegal/angular-developer-mf-1085931', 'emploisenegal.com', '2024-11-29', '2025-01-06 18:00:39.108882', 'Non spécifié', 'Expérience entre 5 ans et 10 ans', 'Contrat proposé\n                             :CDI, CDD - Freelance', 'BOOTSTRAP - CSS3 - CVS - GIT - JAVASCRIPT - JQUERY - LESS - MVC - MYSQL - REST'),
(101, 'DevOps Engineer (M/F)', 'We are looking for  DevOps Engineer  profiles / CVs to pass on to our clients for their future recruitment campaigns. \n   \n  Mission:  \n   \n \n	 Ensure effective Design, Development, Validation and Support activities. \n	 Defining and setting development, test, release, deploy/implementation for DevOps operation. \n	 To play a key role in the overall estimation of work requirements. \n	 Be a key contributor to building efficient programs/ systems. \n	 Application Development and Maintenance. \n	 Knowledge of design principles and fundamentals of architecture. \n	 Knowledge of quality processes and estimation techniques. \n	 Basic understanding of project domain. \n	 Ability to translate functional / nonfunctional requirements...', 'AFRICASHORE', 'Région de :Dakar - Diourbel - Fatick - Kaffrine - Kaolack - Kédougou - Kolda', 'https://www.emploisenegal.com/offre-emploi-senegal/devops-engineer-mf-1085932', 'emploisenegal.com', '2024-11-29', '2025-01-06 18:00:39.112519', 'Non spécifié', 'Expérience entre 5 ans et 10 ans', 'Contrat proposé\n                             :CDI, CDD - Freelance', 'AGILE - APACHE - ARTIFACTORY - AZURE - CVS - DOCKER - DYNATRACE - ECLIPSE - GIT - GITLAB - GROOVY - JAVA - JAVASCRIPT - JBOSS - JENKINS - JIRA - LESS - LINUX - ORACLE - POSTGIS - POSTGRESQL - PYTHON -'),
(102, 'DOTNET Developer (M/F)', 'We are looking for  DOTNET Developer  profiles / CVs to pass on to our clients for their future recruitment campaigns. \n   \n  Mission:  \n   \n \n	 Working within a Team to determine needs and applying / customizing existing technology to meet those needs. \n	 Producing detailed specifications and writing the program codes that perform efficiently. \n	 Write clean, scalable, reusable code using.NET programming languages. \n	 Advanced conceptual understanding of at least one Programming Language. \n	 Advanced conceptual understanding of one database and one Operating System. \n	 Understanding of Software Engineering with practice in at least one project. \n	 Exposure to Design Principles and ability to understand Design...', 'AFRICASHORE', 'Région de :Dakar - Diourbel - Fatick - Kaffrine - Kaolack - Kédougou - Kolda', 'https://www.emploisenegal.com/offre-emploi-senegal/dotnet-developer-mf-1085933', 'emploisenegal.com', '2024-11-29', '2025-01-06 18:00:39.116869', 'Non spécifié', 'Expérience entre 5 ans et 10 ans', 'Contrat proposé\n                             :CDI, CDD - Freelance', 'API - ASP - C# - CSS - CVS - DOTNET - FRONT END - HTML - HTTP - LINUX - MVC - MYSQL - NET - QUERY - REST - SOAP - SQL'),
(103, 'IOS Developer (M/F)', 'We are looking for  iOS Developer  profiles / CVs to pass on to our clients for their future recruitment campaigns. \n   \n  Mission:  \n     \n \n	 Implement, develop, and fix code according to corporate coding standards. \n	 Design and build advanced applications for the iOS platform. \n	 IOS Developer, who is responsible for App development with quality and by following the best practices. \n	 Ability to write scalable and maintainable code. \n	 Coordinate with other team members to ensure that all TMs are in sync. \n	 Be self-starter and goal-oriented with strong analytical and problem-solving skills. \n	 Ability to work cooperatively within a strong diverse technical community to expedite development tasks. \n	 Collaborate...', 'AFRICASHORE', 'Région de :Dakar - Diourbel - Fatick - Kaffrine - Kaolack - Kédougou - Kolda', 'https://www.emploisenegal.com/offre-emploi-senegal/ios-developer-mf-1085934', 'emploisenegal.com', '2024-11-29', '2025-01-06 18:00:39.120397', 'Non spécifié', 'Expérience entre 5 ans et 10 ans', 'Contrat proposé\n                             :CDI, CDD - Freelance', 'AGILE - APP - COCOA - CVS - FOUNDATION - GIT - SWIFT - TMS'),
(104, 'JAVA Developer (M/F)', 'We are looking for  JAVA Developer  profiles / CVs to pass on to our clients for their future recruitment campaigns. \n   \n  Mission:  \n   \n \n	 Working within a Team to determine needs and applying / customizing existing technology to meet those needs. \n	 Producing detailed specifications and writing the program codes that perform efficiently. \n	 Write clean, scalable, reusable code using JAVA Framework sach as Spring, Struts, JSF, GWT etc. \n	 Lead a team closely with complete authority and accountability to deliver high quality software products in a fast-paced environment. \n	 Guide your team members on latest technologies including Java, Spring, Spring-Boot, Angular, Hibernate, Grails, Groovy, Kafka, Redis, Hazelcast...', 'AFRICASHORE', 'Région de :Dakar - Diourbel - Fatick - Kaffrine - Kaolack - Kédougou - Kolda', 'https://www.emploisenegal.com/offre-emploi-senegal/java-developer-mf-1085935', 'emploisenegal.com', '2024-11-29', '2025-01-06 18:00:39.124594', 'Non spécifié', 'Expérience entre 5 ans et 10 ans', 'Contrat proposé\n                             :CDI, CDD - Freelance', 'AGILE - API - BOOTSTRAP - CONFLUENCE - CVS - GIT - GRAILS - GROOVY - GWT - HIBERNATE - HTML - JAVA - JAVASCRIPT - JENKINS - JIRA - JQUERY - JSF - MYSQL - ORACLE - REDIS - SPRING - STRUTS'),
(105, 'JAVA JEE Developer (M/F)', 'We are looking for  JAVA JEE Developer  profiles / CVs to pass on to our clients for their future recruitment campaigns. \n   \n  Mission:  \n   \n \n	 Good exposure to Core Java, MySQL server as DB. \n	 Maintain source code control of all application code, scripts, and database definition language. \n	 Design, Develop, Implement and/or Manage project. \n	 Responsible for development, focusing on designs, coding, testing, quality assurance of complex product features in a development team. \n	 Show initiative and drive topics to resolution in a high level of quality, speed, reliability and efficiency considering the essential non-functional requirements. \n	 Analyzing clients\' requirements and produce technical proposals,...', 'AFRICASHORE', 'Région de :Dakar - Diourbel - Fatick - Kaffrine - Kaolack - Kédougou - Kolda', 'https://www.emploisenegal.com/offre-emploi-senegal/java-jee-developer-mf-1085936', 'emploisenegal.com', '2024-11-29', '2025-01-06 18:00:39.130147', 'Non spécifié', 'Expérience entre 5 ans et 10 ans', 'Contrat proposé\n                             :CDI, CDD - Freelance', 'AGILE - ANGULAR JS - AZURE - BIG DATA - CASSANDRA - COUCHBASE - CSS - CVS - DOCKER - GIT - HADOOP - HIBERNATE - HTML - J2EE - JAVA - JAVA JEE - JAVASCRIPT - JBOSS - JENKINS - MAVEN - MVC - MYSQL - NOS'),
(106, 'JAVASCRIPT Developer (M/F)', 'We are looking for  JAVASCRIPT Developer  profiles / CVs to pass on to our clients for their future recruitment campaigns. \n   \n  Mission:  \n   \n \n	 Primarily responsible for developing software components using Core JavaScript, HTML5 and CSS. \n	 Ensure designs are in compliance with specifications. \n	 Prepare and produce releases of software components. \n	 Help maintain code quality, organization, unit tests and automation. \n	 Support continuous improvement by investigating alternatives and technologies and presenting these for architectural review. \n	 Building sustainable coding that may be used in the future. \n	 Modifying designs and specifications of complex applications. \n	 Analyzing code, requirements, system...', 'AFRICASHORE', 'Région de :Dakar - Diourbel - Fatick - Kaffrine - Kaolack - Kédougou - Kolda', 'https://www.emploisenegal.com/offre-emploi-senegal/javascript-developer-mf-1085937', 'emploisenegal.com', '2024-11-29', '2025-01-06 18:00:39.133807', 'Non spécifié', 'Expérience entre 5 ans et 10 ans', 'Contrat proposé\n                             :CDI, CDD - Freelance', 'ANGULAR JS - API - BACKBONE JS - CSS - CVS - DOJO - HTML - JAVASCRIPT - JENKINS - JQUERY - MONGODB - ORACLE'),
(107, 'KOTLIN Developer (M/F)', 'We are looking for  KOTLIN Developer  profiles / CVs to pass on to our clients for their future recruitment campaigns. \n   \n  Mission:  \n     \n \n	 Working directly with developers and product managers to conceptualize, build, test and release products. \n	 Carefully evaluate the technical trade-offs of every decision. \n	 Work on bug fixing and improving application performance. \n	 Deliver quality code in an efficient manner. \n	 Continuously discover, evaluate, and implement new technologies to maximize development efficiency. \n	 Optimizing performance for the apps and keep up to date on the latest industry trends in the mobile technologies. \n	 Collaborating with UI and UX Designers, as well as Software Testers, to...', 'AFRICASHORE', 'Région de :Dakar - Diourbel - Fatick - Kaffrine - Kaolack - Kédougou - Kolda', 'https://www.emploisenegal.com/offre-emploi-senegal/kotlin-developer-mf-1085938', 'emploisenegal.com', '2024-11-29', '2025-01-06 18:00:39.137272', 'Non spécifié', 'Expérience entre 5 ans et 10 ans', 'Contrat proposé\n                             :CDI, CDD - Freelance', 'AGILE - ANDROID - API - APP - AZURE - CVS - DNS - DOCKER - GIT - JAVA - JENKINS - LOAD BALANCING - MAC - MAVEN - MVVM - OPENSTACK - PAAS - SDK - TCP IP - TDD - UDP - XML'),
