(128, 'Cloud System Integrator (M/F)', 'We are looking for  Cloud System Integrator  profiles / CVs to share with our clients for their future recruitment campaigns. \n   \n  Mission:  \n \n  Create future-proof system architectures for our highly interconnected 4G/5G communication solutions.  \n  Define competitive end-to-end solutions together with top experts from different teams in an international environment.  \n  Demonstrate strong understanding of Networking and security architectures and engage in technical discussions with Network and security architects of large enterprises.  \n  Present both industry and Zscaler technical architecture as it relates to customers and prospects environment and technical requirements.  \n  Ensure that our solutions fit smoothly...', 'AFRICASHORE', 'Région de :Dakar - Diourbel - Fatick - Kaffrine - Kaolack - Kédougou - Kolda', 'https://www.emploisenegal.com/offre-emploi-senegal/cloud-system-integrator-mf-1085959', 'emploisenegal.com', '2024-11-29', '2025-01-06 18:00:39.230904', 'Non spécifié', 'Expérience entre 5 ans et 10 ans', 'Contrat proposé\n                             :CDI, CDD - Freelance', 'AGILE - CVS'),
(129, 'Cyber Security Engineer (M/F)', 'We are looking for  Cyber Security Engineer  profiles / CVs to share with our clients for their future recruitment campaigns. \n   \n  Mission:    \n \n  Act as an internal subject matter expert with respect to CVA scanning and reporting. Assist in maintenance of the enterprise to VMLC (Vulnerability Management Life Cycle) policy and associated VM standard.  \n  Conduct required tasks for the vulnerability scanning program and publish reported vulnerabilities to impacted teams for remediation.  \n  Triage and risk rank vulnerabilities according to severity and exposure. Work with Product and IT teams to risk rank and patch vulnerabilities related to the technology stack. Develop remediation plans for vulnerabilities....', 'AFRICASHORE', 'Région de :Dakar - Diourbel - Fatick - Kaffrine - Kaolack - Kédougou - Kolda', 'https://www.emploisenegal.com/offre-emploi-senegal/cyber-security-engineer-mf-1085960', 'emploisenegal.com', '2024-11-29', '2025-01-06 18:00:39.235843', 'Non spécifié', 'Expérience entre 5 ans et 10 ans', 'Contrat proposé\n                             :CDI, CDD - Freelance', 'CVS - ENDPOINT - IDEAL - JAVASCRIPT - PYTHON - VM'),
(130, 'DATASTAGE Architect (M/F)', 'We are looking for  DATASTAGE Architect  profiles / CVs to share with our clients for their future recruitment campaigns. \n   \n  Mission:    \n \n  Define and supervise all activities within your scope by using and optimising the resources allocated.  \n  Control the implementation of the activities under your responsibility and report on the results.  \n  Responsible for the level of service quality, compliance with standards and the level of safety within the assigned perimeter.  \n  Supervise and monitor of assigned projects (monitoring of workloads, definition of deadlines and delivery milestones, identification of deliverables and work to be carried out, task planning, monitoring of work, management of corrective measures,...', 'AFRICASHORE', 'Région de :Dakar - Diourbel - Fatick - Kaffrine - Kaolack - Kédougou - Kolda', 'https://www.emploisenegal.com/offre-emploi-senegal/datastage-architect-mf-1085961', 'emploisenegal.com', '2024-11-29', '2025-01-06 18:00:39.240578', 'Non spécifié', 'Expérience entre 5 ans et 10 ans', 'Contrat proposé\n                             :CDI, CDD - Freelance', 'AZURE - CVS - DATASTAGE - INFORMATICA - J2EE - JAVA - MONGODB - ORACLE - SQL - TALEND'),
(131, 'GENESYS Architect (M/F)', 'We are looking for  GENESYS Architect  profiles / CVs to share with our clients for their future recruitment campaigns. \n   \n  Mission:  \n \n  Deep and relevant expertise on Genesis Cloud services, along with contact center industry experience.  \n  Be the direct point of technical contact to provide high-quality consultancy for Genesys solutions to customers.  \n  Develop and maintain integration and Cloud solutions.  \n  Knowledge and experience on Cloud computing models (IaaS, PaaS, and SaaS).  \n  Experience with software development and one or more development or scripting languages (e.g. Java. Golang, Python, JavaScript, TypeScript, Bash, PowerShell).  \n  Self-starter with deep hands-on work experience with production...', 'AFRICASHORE', 'Région de :Dakar - Diourbel - Fatick - Kaffrine - Kaolack - Kédougou - Kolda', 'https://www.emploisenegal.com/offre-emploi-senegal/genesys-architect-mf-1085962', 'emploisenegal.com', '2024-11-29', '2025-01-06 18:00:39.246822', 'Non spécifié', 'Expérience entre 5 ans et 10 ans', 'Contrat proposé\n                             :CDI, CDD - Freelance', 'BASH - CVS - GENESYS - JAVA - JAVASCRIPT - PAAS - POWERSHELL - PYTHON - VMWARE'),
(132, 'Network Architect (M/F)', 'We are looking for  Network Architect  profiles / CVs to share with our clients for their future recruitment campaigns. \n   \n  Mission:    \n \n  Deliver Core Backbone Network Designs in alignment with industry best practices.  \n  Deliver Customer Network Designs in alignment with industry best practices.  \n  Support and Alignment with Internal Teams.  \n  Contributor to Automation Stakeholders to deliver speed and accuracy for the enablement of new services.  \n  Perform Core Network Changes.  \n  Manage technical Network solutions and framework of [24]7 Network infrastructure.  \n  Perform Network troubleshooting to isolate and diagnose common Network problems.  \n  Upgrade Network hardware and software components as required...', 'AFRICASHORE', 'Région de :Dakar - Diourbel - Fatick - Kaffrine - Kaolack - Kédougou - Kolda', 'https://www.emploisenegal.com/offre-emploi-senegal/network-architect-mf-1085963', 'emploisenegal.com', '2024-11-29', '2025-01-06 18:00:39.251435', 'Non spécifié', 'Expérience entre 5 ans et 10 ans', 'Contrat proposé\n                             :CDI, CDD - Freelance', 'BGP - CISCO - CVS - DHCP - DNS - ETHERNET - JUNIPER - MPLS - PYTHON - SNMP - TCP IP - WAN'),
(133, 'DBA IMS/DB2 Z/OS(H/F)', 'Nous recherchons des profils / CV de  DBA IMS/DB2 Z/OS (H/F)  pour les transmettre à nos clients dans le cadre de leurs futures campagnes de recrutement. \n		   \n		  Mission :  \n		   \n		 \n		 Assistance au développement technique Z/OS. \n		 Maintenance des projets, support aux analystes Z. \n		 Mise en œuvre opérationnelle des projets de développement. \n		 Assurer le maintien en conditions opérationnelles. \n		 Réaliser la maintenance (mise à jour de versions, patchs management). \n		 Construction de nouveaux socles techniques. \n		 Traitement et incidents de niveau 3. \n		 Suivi et analyse des performances.', 'AFRICASHORE', 'Région de :Dakar - Diourbel - Fatick - Kaffrine - Kaolack - Kédougou - Kolda', 'https://www.emploisenegal.com/offre-emploi-senegal/dba-imsdb2-zoshf-1085964', 'emploisenegal.com', '2024-11-29', '2025-01-06 18:00:39.256439', 'Non spécifié', 'Expérience entre 5 ans et 10 ans', 'Contrat proposé\n                             :CDI, CDD - Freelance', 'ASSEMBLEUR - COBOL - DB2 - FORTRAN - ISPF - JCL - SAS - SDSF - TCP IP - TSO - TWS - VSAM'),
(134, 'Z/OS System Engineer Senior Storage(H/F)', 'Nous recherchons des profils / CV de  Z/OS System Engineer Senior Storage (H/F)  pour les transmettre à nos clients dans le cadre de leurs futures campagnes de recrutement.     Mission :  \n		   \n		 \n		 Mise en œuvre, suivi et gestion technique opérationnelle des opérations, \n		 Enrichissement et rechargement des environnements Mainframe z/OS d’homologation et de répétition de bascules. \n		 Définition des partitions (création du socle, SGBD, middlewares transactionnels et flux, service techniques, sécurité), clonage et alimentation de données, interopération avec les environnements mainframe et distribués (non mainframe)....', 'AFRICASHORE', 'Région de :Dakar - Diourbel - Fatick - Kaffrine - Kaolack - Kédougou - Kolda', 'https://www.emploisenegal.com/offre-emploi-senegal/zos-system-engineer-senior-storagehf-1085965', 'emploisenegal.com', '2024-11-29', '2025-01-06 18:00:39.265542', 'Non spécifié', 'Expérience entre 5 ans et 10 ans', 'Contrat proposé\n                             :CDI, CDD - Freelance', 'CICS - DB2 - IBM - JCL - MVS - TSO - VSAM - ZOS'),
(135, 'Ingénieur Système Z/OS Middleware (H/F)', 'Nous recherchons des profils / CV de  Ingénieur Système Z/OS Middleware (H/F  )  pour les transmettre à nos clients dans le cadre de leurs futures campagnes de recrutement. \n		   \n		  Mission :  \n		   \n		 \n		 Ingénieur système Z/OS expérimenté, être capable d\'installer, de paramétrer, d\'activer et d\'exécuter tant l\'investigation et la résolution des problèmes des produits habituellement utilisés dans un environnement z/OS. \n		 Equipe en charge de la gestion d\'un environnement mainframe (HW / SW) incluant la sécurité associée (RACF), le stockage (DASD, Tape, B&R, DRP), la conformité, la mé...', 'AFRICASHORE', 'Région de :Dakar - Diourbel - Fatick - Kaffrine - Kaolack - Kédougou - Kolda', 'https://www.emploisenegal.com/offre-emploi-senegal/ingenieur-systeme-zos-middleware-hf-1085966', 'emploisenegal.com', '2024-11-29', '2025-01-06 18:00:39.273034', 'Non spécifié', 'Expérience entre 5 ans et 10 ans', 'Contrat proposé\n                             :CDI, CDD - Freelance', 'ASSEMBLEUR - COBOL - JAVA - LDAP - NETVIEW - TCP IP - TWS - VTAM');
